<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Mugen, you WILL UNDERSTAND the book. I didn&apos;t know anything, or not much about North Korea, and it was an eye opening book, with beautiful albeit pain<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Mugen, you WILL UNDERSTAND the book. I didn't know anything, or not much about North Korea, and it was an eye opening book, with beautiful albeit painful narrations of several people and families through the years. The writer is very clear and writes with skill, I couldn't stop listening to it (I got it on audio).<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
