<div id="review_255957900" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/255957900" />
    <a title="Michael Gerald" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/7329074-michael-gerald"><img alt="Michael Gerald" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1611498497p2/7329074.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/255957900?book_show_action=true">Jan 03, 2012</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Michael Gerald" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Michael Gerald" href="/user/show/7329074-michael-gerald">Michael Gerald</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780385523912" href="/book/show/7667369-nothing-to-envy">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer255957900" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15163643153269147761">If you thought that George Orwell&apos;s satires Animal Farm and 1984 are just works of fiction, think again. Look at a map and find North Korea. That&apos;s a present-day, real-life Animal Farm.<br/><br/>But, since it&apos;s written by an American, it should still be read with a grain of salt.</span>
  <span id="freeText15163643153269147761" style="display:none">If you thought that George Orwell's satires Animal Farm and 1984 are just works of fiction, think again. Look at a map and find North Korea. That's a present-day, real-life Animal Farm.<br /><br />But, since it's written by an American, it should still be read with a grain of salt.</span>
